  "code": "%%{IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\n    direction LR\n    classDef lifecycle fill:#ffffff,stroke:#5d5fef,stroke-width:2px,color:#222\n\n    state \"En Progreso\\nEstaCompletada = false\\nMontoActual < MontoObjetivo\" as EnProgreso\n    state \"Completada\\nEstaCompletada = true\\nMontoActual ≥ MontoObjetivo\" as Completada\n    state \"Eliminada\\nRegistro físico borrado\" as Eliminada\n\n    class EnProgreso,Completada,Eliminada lifecycle\n\n    [IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream] --> EnProgreso : CrearMeta(IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream) / inicializarMeta(IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n    [IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker] --> Completada : CrearMeta(IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream) [IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker] / inicializarMeta(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n\n    %% Ciclo natural de ahorro\n    EnProgreso --> EnProgreso : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\\n/ ActualizarMontos(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n    EnProgreso --> Completada : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\\n/ ActualizarMontos(IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)\n\n    Completada --> Completada : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\\n/ MantenerCierre(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n    Completada --> EnProgreso : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\\n/ AjustarMontos(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n\n    %% Actualizaciones manuales vía PUT\n    EnProgreso --> Completada : ActualizarMeta(IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\\n[IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController]\\n/ PersistirCambios(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n    Completada --> EnProgreso : ActualizarMeta(IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\\n[IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker]\\n/ PersistirCambios(IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n\n    %% Borrado definitivo\n    EnProgreso --> Eliminada : EliminarMeta(IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController) / BorrarRegistro(IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\n    Completada --> Eliminada : EliminarMeta(IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream) / BorrarRegistro(IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker)\n    Eliminada --> [IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream]\n\n    note right of EnProgreso\n        Estado operacional por defecto.\n        Las contribuciones suman al monto y\n        recalculan el progreso.\n    end note\n\n    note right of Completada\n        Se marca cuando MontoActual\n        alcanza o supera el objetivo.\n        Puede reabrirse con ajustes manuales.\n    end note\n",
